<template>
  <el-breadcrumb separator="/">
  <template v-for="item in breadcrumbs" :key="item.name">
    <el-breadcrumb-item :to="{ path: '/' }">{{item.name}}</el-breadcrumb-item>
  </template>
   
  </el-breadcrumb>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    props:{
         breadcrumbs:{
            type:Array,
            default:()=>{

            }
         }
    }
}
</script>
